==English==
===Adjective===
'''mediocre'''
# [[Ordinary]]: not extraordinary; not [[special]], [[exceptional]], or [[great]]; of [[medium]] quality.
#:''I'm pretty good at tennis but only '''mediocre''' at raquetball.''

